@startuml seq-fluxo-completo
title Fluxo completo - Registrar lancamento ate consultar saldo

actor Comerciante
participant "Front" as Front
participant "API Lancamentos" as ApiLanc
participant "API Relatorios" as ApiRel
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
queue SQS
participant "Worker" as Worker

== Write path (RF01) ==
Comerciante -> Front: Novo lancamento
Front -> ApiLanc: POST /api/lancamentos
ApiLanc -> DB: Salva lancamento
ApiLanc -> SQS: LancamentoCriado
ApiLanc --> Front: 201 Created

== Async (RF04/RF05) ==
SQS -> Worker: Evento
Worker -> DB: Recalcula saldo do dia
Worker -> DB: UPSERT saldos_diarios

== Read path (RF07) ==
Comerciante -> Front: Consulta dia
Front -> ApiRel: GET /api/relatorios/{dia}
ApiRel -> DB: SELECT saldo
ApiRel --> Front: 200 ou 204
Front --> Comerciante: Saldo consolidado

@enduml
